*---------------------------------------------------------------------*
* Eligibility decision (FINAL RULE)
*---------------------------------------------------------------------*
* 1. Orders WITHOUT CMXS → ALWAYS eligible
* 2. Orders WITH CMXS    → eligible ONLY if changed inside window
*---------------------------------------------------------------------*
IF lv_cmxs_active = abap_false.
  lv_eligible = abap_true.

ELSEIF lv_has_cdhdr_change = abap_true
   OR  lv_has_jcds_change  = abap_true.
  lv_eligible = abap_true.

ELSE.
  RETURN. " CMXS + no changes → skip
ENDIF.